1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:08,570
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

2
00:00:08,745 --> 00:00:16,982
<i>Even if you get lost, let's start walking</i>

3
00:00:17,220 --> 00:00:19,211
<i>One more time</i>

4
00:00:22,225 --> 00:00:25,991
<i>Are you really happy</i>

5
00:00:26,063 --> 00:00:29,430
<i>when you're always meeting</i>
<i>to someone's expectations?</i>

6
00:00:29,633 --> 00:00:33,194
<i>Even if you change to</i>
<i>who you really wanna be</i>

7
00:00:33,570 --> 00:00:36,937
<i>Will you always have a great smile?</i>

8
00:00:37,007 --> 00:00:44,436
<i>Dreaming of only "the beginning,"</i>
<i>I wake up</i>

9
00:00:44,514 --> 00:00:53,650
<i>and someday, I'll live on my own.</i>

10
00:00:53,724 --> 00:01:01,756
<i>Yes, precious things are never in shape</i>

11
00:01:01,998 --> 00:01:08,836
<i>You never know what it is</i>
<i>when you get it or lose it</i>

12
00:01:08,905 --> 00:01:16,971
<i>Yeah, turn your sadness into kindness,</i>
<i>your uniqueness into strength</i>

13
00:01:17,280 --> 00:01:25,745
<i>Even if you get lost,</i>
<i>let's start walking</i>

14
00:01:25,822 --> 00:01:27,847
<i>One more time</i>

15
00:01:54,428 --> 00:01:55,793
Summoning Jutsu!

16
00:01:57,598 --> 00:01:59,566
This time for sure, the frog will...

17
00:02:11,879 --> 00:02:14,609
What's a frog anyway?!

18
00:02:14,682 --> 00:02:16,775
From which stage do you
call it a frog?!

19
00:02:20,955 --> 00:02:26,791
<i>Live or Die.</i>
<i>Risk it All to Win it All!</i>

20
00:02:32,266 --> 00:02:35,133
Hey! Hold up a hope
on me a bit, would you?!

21
00:02:42,643 --> 00:02:45,271
Whew... he collapsed again...

22
00:02:46,347 --> 00:02:47,939
<i>That's no surprise...</i>

23
00:02:48,215 --> 00:02:53,380
<i>For three weeks, he's continued</i>
<i>his training on guts alone...</i>

24
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:20,972
Lord Hokage

25
00:03:23,017 --> 00:03:24,644
Anko, is it...?

26
00:03:30,858 --> 00:03:33,588
I'm sorry, I'm...

27
00:03:34,161 --> 00:03:38,621
Regretting returning alive
from the Forest of Death?

28
00:03:41,669 --> 00:03:47,539
That's a needless thing because you and
Orochimaru have no connection at all.

29
00:03:52,146 --> 00:03:58,574
There is no Shinobi who can compete
against that guy in Hidden Leaf Village.

30
00:04:01,822 --> 00:04:06,486
Even if I was the one to face him...

31
00:04:07,428 --> 00:04:10,693
If the Fourth Hokage were still alive...

32
00:04:11,198 --> 00:04:12,961
Don't say that.

33
00:04:13,401 --> 00:04:17,838
He already saved this village and died...

34
00:04:18,806 --> 00:04:26,008
That's a story from 13 years ago
He's no longer here.

35
00:04:26,414 --> 00:04:29,383
We have to do something
with our power.

36
00:04:30,985 --> 00:04:31,974
Yes.

37
00:04:34,855 --> 00:04:37,653
I'm going to get some fresh air...

38
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:48,329
Don't blame yourself.

39
00:04:59,346 --> 00:05:01,780
C'mon, open your eyes already.

40
00:05:05,786 --> 00:05:07,720
W-What's that...?

41
00:05:08,022 --> 00:05:11,549
To be clear, you have no sense.

42
00:05:11,625 --> 00:05:13,593
Oh! Pervy Sage!

43
00:05:13,928 --> 00:05:16,419
After you've been training for 3 weeks,
you are still this level.

44
00:05:16,497 --> 00:05:19,091
If you continue like this it's pointless.

45
00:05:19,734 --> 00:05:23,431
That's not how it is!
I'm doing this with all my might!

46
00:05:23,504 --> 00:05:28,134
I understand that, if you really want
to succeed at Summoning Jutsu,

47
00:05:28,209 --> 00:05:31,178
you have to do it like you're going
to die or it's no good at all.

48
00:05:31,378 --> 00:05:32,845
That's what I'm doing!

49
00:05:32,913 --> 00:05:35,211
I drill my Chakra every day
like I'm going to die.

50
00:05:35,282 --> 00:05:38,410
If you have time to complain about it,
teach me a trick or something!

51
00:05:38,919 --> 00:05:41,752
A trick, huh... A trick.

52
00:05:41,856 --> 00:05:44,051
What?! You're going to teach me?

53
00:05:45,159 --> 00:05:47,024
You need to risk your life on it.

54
00:05:47,461 --> 00:05:48,519
L-Life?

55
00:05:49,096 --> 00:05:52,623
It's not a joke.
Even so, will you do it?

56
00:05:52,767 --> 00:05:57,261
O-Of course!
I always risk my life!

57
00:05:59,006 --> 00:05:59,904
I see...

58
00:05:59,974 --> 00:06:00,838
Huh?

59
00:06:01,008 --> 00:06:02,737
Well then, follow me.

60
00:06:16,323 --> 00:06:19,019
What are we doing at a place like this?

61
00:06:19,393 --> 00:06:21,987
You're not gonna peek again,
are you?

62
00:06:24,431 --> 00:06:29,232
Well, that would be nice,
but today it's a bath.

63
00:06:29,303 --> 00:06:31,066
First, we purify our bodies...

64
00:06:32,339 --> 00:06:33,169
Huh?

65
00:06:40,881 --> 00:06:43,907
<i>There's something strange going on...</i>

66
00:06:46,153 --> 00:06:50,852
This is such a nice bath.

67
00:06:51,192 --> 00:06:55,424
Like heaven... Truly heavenly...

68
00:06:59,300 --> 00:07:01,063
Hey, Pervy Sage.

69
00:07:01,468 --> 00:07:02,799
I'm Toad Sage.

70
00:07:02,937 --> 00:07:08,307
Whatever, but how are taking
a bath and Summoning related?

71
00:07:11,645 --> 00:07:13,806
Hey, hey, hey, hey...!

72
00:07:15,082 --> 00:07:17,016
What is it?!

73
00:07:17,218 --> 00:07:18,685
Hey, Naruto.

74
00:07:18,853 --> 00:07:19,717
Huh?

75
00:07:20,554 --> 00:07:23,546
Is there something you want to eat?

76
00:07:27,661 --> 00:07:29,526
I'm going to eat!

77
00:07:31,599 --> 00:07:36,502
It's good! If the training is like this,
I'll do it every day!

78
00:07:36,937 --> 00:07:40,270
Eat up! Because this is the last...

79
00:07:40,341 --> 00:07:41,035
Huh?

80
00:07:42,042 --> 00:07:45,102
No, nothing. Anyway, eat!
Eat a lot!

81
00:07:45,379 --> 00:07:47,813
Like there's no looking back!

82
00:07:50,584 --> 00:07:54,418
I don't know what's going on,
but I should eat, right? Okay!

83
00:08:02,563 --> 00:08:04,724
Seconds! The next one is <i>miso</i> flavor too!

84
00:08:04,932 --> 00:08:05,762
Gotcha!

85
00:08:09,570 --> 00:08:10,264
One more!

86
00:08:10,638 --> 00:08:11,366
Coming right up!

87
00:08:11,438 --> 00:08:12,996
This time <i>miso char siu!</i>

88
00:08:13,073 --> 00:08:13,767
Yeah!

89
00:08:16,443 --> 00:08:18,070
I ate, I ate.

90
00:08:18,512 --> 00:08:20,207
Thank you, Pervy Sage...

91
00:08:23,350 --> 00:08:24,840
What?!

92
00:08:25,286 --> 00:08:26,253
Thanks for your patronage!

93
00:08:33,894 --> 00:08:35,384
I won't even get blood from it...

94
00:08:36,864 --> 00:08:38,889
Yo, are you full?

95
00:08:41,135 --> 00:08:42,932
Don't mess with me, Pervy Sage!

96
00:08:43,003 --> 00:08:45,836
Weren't you treating me
with the meal!

97
00:08:46,273 --> 00:08:49,037
Fool! Who said that
I was treating you?!

98
00:08:49,543 --> 00:08:52,137
Aren't you a grown up?! Bastard!

99
00:08:52,379 --> 00:08:55,644
By the by, Naruto,
isn't there a girl that you like?

100
00:08:56,317 --> 00:08:57,147
Huh?

101
00:08:57,251 --> 00:09:00,778
I asked if you have a lovely girl?

102
00:09:01,088 --> 00:09:04,319
Well... you could say she's there,
you could say I like her...

103
00:09:04,391 --> 00:09:06,188
You could say it's Sakura.

104
00:09:06,493 --> 00:09:07,357
So there is?

105
00:09:07,428 --> 00:09:09,157
It's Sakura!

106
00:09:09,229 --> 00:09:13,996
Okay! Then go and
hug that girl tight!

107
00:09:14,068 --> 00:09:17,435
What?!

108
00:09:17,504 --> 00:09:18,937
Is that a part of the training?

109
00:09:19,006 --> 00:09:21,031
Well, close enough.

110
00:09:21,475 --> 00:09:23,909
Okay! Right away...

111
00:09:24,378 --> 00:09:27,779
But if I do that, Sakura will...

112
00:09:28,449 --> 00:09:33,443
No! This is training too!
I have to do it or I won't be strong...

113
00:09:33,988 --> 00:09:36,650
But if I do that, Sakura will...

114
00:09:37,024 --> 00:09:39,390
For a while she won't talk to me...

115
00:09:39,593 --> 00:09:42,528
No! If I'm going to master
Summoning Jutsu,

116
00:09:42,596 --> 00:09:44,086
this can't be helped!

117
00:09:44,264 --> 00:09:46,494
But... Sakura will...

118
00:09:47,301 --> 00:09:49,997
No! But...

119
00:09:50,270 --> 00:09:52,101
Hurry up and go

120
00:09:58,012 --> 00:09:59,104
What do you want?

121
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:02,142
No, uh... well...

122
00:10:02,416 --> 00:10:04,043
If it's money you want,
I won't lend it to you.

123
00:10:04,551 --> 00:10:06,712
I may not look it,
but I'm stingy with money.

124
00:10:07,121 --> 00:10:08,986
No, that's not it...

125
00:10:09,189 --> 00:10:10,451
Well...

126
00:10:11,158 --> 00:10:16,186
<i>Uh, if I tell her it's for my training,</i>
<i>she's sure to beat me.</i>

127
00:10:16,897 --> 00:10:18,762
If there's nothing you want,
then I'll go home.

128
00:10:19,433 --> 00:10:20,491
W-Wait a minute!

129
00:10:21,502 --> 00:10:22,469
Oh...

130
00:10:25,672 --> 00:10:28,402
<i>This is it!</i>
<i>This is my chance!</i>

131
00:10:28,809 --> 00:10:30,572
<i>Sakura! I'm sorry!</i>

132
00:10:32,746 --> 00:10:33,838
Hey!

133
00:10:33,914 --> 00:10:35,381
What are you doing?!

134
00:10:40,721 --> 00:10:42,245
Cha!

135
00:10:43,957 --> 00:10:47,256
Ow... Ouch...

136
00:10:52,633 --> 00:10:55,431
This is a part of being young...

137
00:10:59,640 --> 00:11:02,609
Hey, if I do this I'll really get a frog

138
00:11:02,676 --> 00:11:05,509
Yes, that's a definite.

139
00:11:06,080 --> 00:11:07,172
Really?

140
00:11:07,347 --> 00:11:09,645
Is there anything you've left undone?

141
00:11:09,850 --> 00:11:10,646
Huh?

142
00:11:11,452 --> 00:11:12,476
None?

143
00:11:12,553 --> 00:11:13,577
What are you talking about...?

144
00:11:23,664 --> 00:11:27,498
<i>To pull out enormous Chakra</i>
<i>and use it.</i>

145
00:11:28,001 --> 00:11:30,299
<i>It is certain that it is difficult</i>
<i>to have the control to do it...</i>

146
00:11:31,038 --> 00:11:34,565
<i>It is also certain that this body</i>
<i>is a vessel too small</i>

147
00:11:34,641 --> 00:11:36,973
<i>to absorb the Nine Tailed Fox Chakra...</i>

148
00:11:37,778 --> 00:11:39,643
<i>It's likely that Naruto's body normally</i>
<i>tends to reject</i>

149
00:11:39,713 --> 00:11:43,080
<i>the strength of the Nine Tailed Fox</i>
<i>in order to avoid too much strain.</i>

150
00:11:45,686 --> 00:11:47,916
<i>If the excitement of danger and</i>
<i>emotion are the key</i>

151
00:11:47,988 --> 00:11:50,513
<i>to drawing out the</i>
<i>Nine Tailed Fox's Chakra...</i>

152
00:11:50,591 --> 00:11:54,288
<i>he has to learn physically until</i>
<i>he can automatically use that key.</i>

153
00:11:55,262 --> 00:11:58,231
<i>Nothing personal...</i>
<i>Fourth Hokage!</i>

154
00:12:13,914 --> 00:12:17,372
Huh? Where... is this?

155
00:12:18,252 --> 00:12:19,150
Stand up!

156
00:12:20,053 --> 00:12:22,248
W-What's going on?!

157
00:12:22,422 --> 00:12:24,014
Your training ends here.

158
00:12:24,258 --> 00:12:26,283
Huh? I haven't done anything yet...!

159
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:27,224
Naruto!

160
00:12:27,728 --> 00:12:29,787
Go die and come back.

161
00:12:30,564 --> 00:12:31,326
Die?

162
00:12:31,598 --> 00:12:36,126
From within the dreadfulness of death,
squeeze out enormous Chakra!

163
00:12:36,803 --> 00:12:40,739
Experience it with your own body,
and grasp the technique of it!

164
00:12:41,308 --> 00:12:45,005
If you don't want to die,
do something about it yourself... Got it?

165
00:12:59,660 --> 00:13:06,498
<i>Now...we'll see if the strength given</i>
<i>to you is really yours.</i>

166
00:13:12,506 --> 00:13:15,031
<i>If I don't grab onto this... I'll die!</i>

167
00:13:19,580 --> 00:13:20,376
<i>Now!</i>

168
00:13:25,018 --> 00:13:26,280
<i>It's impossible...</i>

169
00:13:26,954 --> 00:13:30,185
<i>This rock surface is slippery</i>
<i>from the seepage of the waterfall.</i>

170
00:13:30,691 --> 00:13:34,752
<i>Besides, falling in that speed</i>
<i>with the control of Chakra that you have,</i>

171
00:13:34,828 --> 00:13:37,194
<i>you can't cling to the rock.</i>

172
00:13:38,732 --> 00:13:41,098
<i>Naruto, after this...</i>

173
00:13:41,168 --> 00:13:43,500
<i>you can only depend on</i>
<i>the Chakra of the Nine Tailed Fox.</i>

174
00:13:44,404 --> 00:13:48,932
<i>Open up the key...</i>
<i>This time from your side!</i>

175
00:13:50,877 --> 00:13:54,313
<i>If I go on like this!</i>
<i>If I go on like this! I'll seriously die!</i>

176
00:13:57,851 --> 00:13:58,545
<i>Die!</i>

177
00:14:01,622 --> 00:14:02,748
<i>Die...</i>

178
00:14:11,366 --> 00:14:14,699
Today, we'll have
a history lesson outside.

179
00:14:15,169 --> 00:14:20,266
As you know, this rock face has
the faces of the Hokage line.

180
00:14:20,742 --> 00:14:22,642
In order from the left,
they're lined up fom the First,

181
00:14:23,611 --> 00:14:30,107
the Second...
the Third... and the Fourth.

182
00:14:32,019 --> 00:14:35,216
<i>So different from the present old man.</i>

183
00:14:35,523 --> 00:14:37,081
<i>Especially the receding hairline...</i>

184
00:14:40,762 --> 00:14:44,129
Iruka Sensei! Who's the Fifth?

185
00:14:44,298 --> 00:14:45,230
Hmm?

186
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:48,194
Well, that hasn't been decided yet...

187
00:14:49,003 --> 00:14:50,937
Perhaps it's your teacher here!

188
00:14:52,807 --> 00:14:59,144
Hmm... Weaving an occasional joke
to make for a relaxing lesson, Iruka?

189
00:14:59,447 --> 00:15:00,709
L-Lord Hokage!

190
00:15:00,782 --> 00:15:02,079
Oh, it's the Third.

191
00:15:02,283 --> 00:15:04,774
Hey! Old man!
What did you come to do?

192
00:15:05,019 --> 00:15:08,477
I wanted to see the rock faces too.

193
00:15:08,656 --> 00:15:11,853
You've come at a good time.
Over this way, my lord.

194
00:15:21,335 --> 00:15:25,032
This is the real man of
the third rock face!

195
00:15:25,239 --> 00:15:26,968
The Third Hokage!

196
00:15:27,975 --> 00:15:31,206
The third was called the strongest,
a genius,

197
00:15:31,279 --> 00:15:34,578
called "professor" among
past Hokage!

198
00:15:34,749 --> 00:15:36,273
- What?!
- Huh?!

199
00:15:36,918 --> 00:15:39,910
Hey! Iruka, don't say it
in the past tense.

200
00:15:40,788 --> 00:15:41,880
S-Sorry.

201
00:15:41,956 --> 00:15:43,423
Are you really strong?

202
00:15:43,491 --> 00:15:45,083
Yeah, you don't look it!

203
00:15:45,193 --> 00:15:47,525
<i>Yep! That's right!</i>

204
00:15:48,362 --> 00:15:49,294
Enough!

205
00:15:49,363 --> 00:15:55,063
To take over the name of Hokage
means you're the strongest in this village!

206
00:15:55,136 --> 00:15:57,696
Okay! I'm going to become
the Fifth Hokage!

207
00:15:57,772 --> 00:16:00,297
After all I'm really strong,
and handsome too!

208
00:16:01,676 --> 00:16:04,008
It won't work with
the scores you have now!

209
00:16:07,348 --> 00:16:09,509
You've got a lot of confidence!

210
00:16:10,184 --> 00:16:13,449
You all are quite young,
unlike me!

211
00:16:13,921 --> 00:16:18,517
There might be someone who will
take the name of Hokage in this group.

212
00:16:19,060 --> 00:16:20,891
You only have one life!

213
00:16:21,028 --> 00:16:23,292
Don't choose an impossible road.

214
00:16:23,965 --> 00:16:26,763
It doesn't matter if you live as
you like and die as you like.

215
00:16:27,435 --> 00:16:28,663
However...

216
00:16:34,609 --> 00:16:37,169
no matter what route you take,

217
00:16:37,245 --> 00:16:40,339
remember to protect the
people important to you!

218
00:16:40,448 --> 00:16:42,211
Important people?

219
00:16:42,917 --> 00:16:48,184
That you acknowledge...
trust and love from your heart.

220
00:16:48,389 --> 00:16:50,619
Do you have people like that?

221
00:16:50,825 --> 00:16:54,818
Y-Yeah... Dad and Mom...

222
00:16:55,129 --> 00:16:57,825
and I hate him a little,
but my big brother too.

223
00:16:58,032 --> 00:17:00,398
And...
my dog Gonta...

224
00:17:00,902 --> 00:17:02,631
For me, it's friends!

225
00:17:03,771 --> 00:17:04,635
Me too!

226
00:17:07,909 --> 00:17:10,275
Lord Hokage, you have
people like that too?

227
00:17:10,845 --> 00:17:13,143
Yes, of course I do!

228
00:17:13,281 --> 00:17:15,476
Really! Who, who?

229
00:17:15,850 --> 00:17:19,786
I have my grandchild...
Konohamaru over there and...

230
00:17:23,858 --> 00:17:27,726
All of the people in this village!

231
00:17:40,174 --> 00:17:44,907
<i>Like you did too, once...</i>

232
00:18:08,736 --> 00:18:09,600
Huh?!

233
00:18:28,556 --> 00:18:31,992
<i>This feeling... It's that Chakra...</i>

234
00:18:52,113 --> 00:18:53,171
This is...

235
00:18:53,514 --> 00:18:57,109
Seal

236
00:19:05,259 --> 00:19:07,557
<i>I-It's huge... What is it?</i>

237
00:19:08,963 --> 00:19:13,127
Hey kid, come closer!

238
00:19:19,640 --> 00:19:25,340
I want to eat and kill you,
but this gate won't open...

239
00:19:25,479 --> 00:19:28,642
Bloody spell that seals...

240
00:19:30,284 --> 00:19:31,273
You're...

241
00:19:34,422 --> 00:19:36,151
the Nine-Tailed Fox!

242
00:19:37,491 --> 00:19:42,087
<i>I see... the red Chakra</i>
<i>was this guy's Chakra.</i>

243
00:19:43,130 --> 00:19:48,124
For you to approach me...

244
